data.description: $15,000 PRICE REDUCTION!!!  Darling, well-taken care of tri-level starter home in a great part of town and for a great price!  Lots of updates.  Newer kitchen with stainless steel appliance package and quartz countertops.  Newer carpet.  Laminate floors in living/kitchen areas.  Huge covered patio out back for BBQ's in any weather or just to sit outside and enjoy your drink of choice.  Includes a new water heater as well as a water softening system.  2-car garage w/RV parking.  Convenient location, right off of 8000 West.  Straight shot north out to SR-201, or a few blocks south to Smith's, Walmart, and other shops and restaurants.  ADU is attached to the back side of the garage, behind the flex space, with an outside entrance.  Consists of 1 bedroom (maybe 10x10?), a tiny 3/4 bath, and a small kitchenette.  (See ADU Remarks for additional info.)
